rows.label: qst710203_msg0001
rows.name:
They seem to be swimming
around happily enough...

rows.label: qst710203_msg0002
rows.name:
Yes, indeed! Spirited enough
to match the dauntless
courage of Iiran knights!

rows.label: qst710203_msg0003
rows.name:
The people of the capital
will be most pleased!

rows.label: qst710203_msg0004
rows.name:
Wadatsumi, what do you
think about the fish?

rows.label: qst710203_msg0005
rows.name:
They seem grown enough to eat,
by my assessment. If I can be so
bold, may I suggest carpaccio?

rows.label: qst710203_msg0007
rows.name:
Terrific! Well then, I'll raise
them carefully so they'll be the
prettiest fish you've ever seen!

rows.label: qst710203_msg0009
rows.name: OK, next up is the front moat.

rows.label: qst710203_msg0010
rows.name:
Used to be full of fish till the
Holy Grail attacked the capital.
The moat was teeming with life.

rows.label: qst710203_msg0011
rows.name:
I know you don't know me or
anything, but I'm really
counting on you to help.

rows.label: qst710203_msg0012
rows.name:
Will you catch some fish we
can use to restock the moat?

rows.label: qst710203_msg0013
rows.name:
It'll be such a lift to the atmosphere
of the area if we could get the moat
back to how it used to be.

rows.label: qst710203_msg0014
rows.name:
I really do hope you'll
be able to help.
